data.description: 2.875% VA ASSUMABLE LOAN WITH $452,834.23 BALANCE - Welcome home to this one-level Rambler, brimming with updates in the heart of Alexandria! With 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a large backyard, there's room for everyone. New exterior siding, and laminate flooring throughout. New kitchen features all stainless steel appliances, tile floors, and an adjacent dining area. 4 well-appointed bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The fully fenced, flat backyard is a perfect spot to enjoy a cup of hot cider around the built-in fire pit or from the patio. You'll love the privacy the mature trees and landscaping provide. The driveway has room for 3 cars and extra parking on the street. HVAC installed 2019, Roof installed 2021. Less than 1 mile to Rt 1, and convenient access to Ft Belvoir, Mount Vernon, Huntley Meadows Park, the GW Memorial Parkway, and Old Town Alexandria.
